videos.description: Jae Crowder forces a Clippers timeout with a 3-pointer and then lets the LA bench hear about it.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Crowder lets the Clippers' bench hear it after a 3) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Crowder lets the Clippers' bench hear it after a 3

videos.description: Deandre Ayton follows the miss with the bucket and has words with the Clippers while walking back to the huddle.

videos.headline: Ayton has words for the Clippers after putback

videos.description: Cameron Payne picks up a technical foul after getting into it with Terance Mann.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Payne has words with Clippers after being T'd up) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Payne has words with Clippers after being T'd up

videos.description: Devin Booker scores nine points in the first quarter, including these two impressive shots over Ivica Zubac.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker hot early with impressive first-quarter buckets) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker hot early with impressive first-quarter buckets

videos.description: Chris Paul lobs it up to Deandre Ayton who curves it into the hoop.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 finds Ayton for smooth alley-oop) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 finds Ayton for smooth alley-oop

videos.description: Paul George breaks a long Clippers scoring drought by dribbling through multiple Suns defenders and hitting a jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (PG dribbles through traffic to end Clippers' drought) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: PG dribbles through traffic to end Clippers' drought

videos.description: Cameron Payne steps back way behind the line and knocks down the 3-pointer with Terance Mann right on him.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Payne knocks down tough 3 with hand in his face) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Payne knocks down tough 3 with hand in his face

videos.description: Mikal Bridges denies Reggie Jackson at the rim sending his shot all the way out to half court.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bridges rises for sensational block on Jackson) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bridges rises for sensational block on Jackson

videos.description: Chris Paul goes between his legs then calmly knocks down the midrange jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 shows off slick handles before the jumper) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 shows off slick handles before the jumper

videos.description: Reggie Jackson brings the Clippers within five after knocking down a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jackson gets Staples Center on its feet with a 3) 2021/06/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jackson gets Staples Center on its feet with a 3

videos.description: Mike Breen says a stoic Kawhi Leonard is going crazy after Paul George knocks down the jumper.
